<!-- Chinese Executive Summary -->
<div style="border:1px solid #166534; background:#dcfce7; border-radius:12px; padding:14px; margin:0 0 14px 0;">
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#166534; margin:0 0 8px 0; letter-spacing:.2px; font-weight:700;">中文摘要</div>
  <p style="margin:0 0 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.65; color:#111;">NVDA 在 CES 2026 發布 Blackwell Ultra，推理效能提升 <strong>2.5 倍</strong>、能效改善 <strong>+40%</strong>，帶動 AI 晶片板塊齊漲：NVDA +4.2%、AMD +2.8%、AVGO +1.9%。</p>
  <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.65; color:#111;"><strong>這不是新品新聞，而是推理成本曲線下移的訊號。</strong>市場重算的是：雲端是否會因效能/瓦改善而前置部署。</p>
  <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.65; color:#111;">本文把「推理成本曲線」拆成 <strong>4 個可驗證變數</strong>，並提供兩週事件時間軸與情境策略表。會員版包含完整 Ticker Playbook 與同業估值比較。</p>
</div>

<!-- English Executive Summary -->
<div style="border:1px solid #dcfce7; background:#f0fdf4; border-radius:12px; padding:14px; margin:0 0 14px 0;">
  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#166534; margin:0 0 8px 0; letter-spacing:.2px; font-weight:600;">EXECUTIVE SUMMARY</div>
  <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#333;">
    NVIDIA's CES 2026 keynote unveiled Blackwell Ultra with 2.5x inference performance and 40% better energy efficiency, triggering a sector-wide rally. NVDA surged 4.2% on 1.8x average volume, while AMD gained 2.8% on MI400 Azure deal momentum and AVGO rose 1.9% on AI ASIC expansion narrative.
  </p>
  <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#333;">
    The market isn't pricing a product launch—it's repricing the inference cost curve. Key variables: (1) whether inference unit costs drop another leg, (2) whether power/cooling bottlenecks ease, (3) whether cloud capex gets pulled forward.
  </p>
  <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#333;">
    NVDA trades at 52.3x P/E vs peer median 41.95x, a 25% premium. Watch: AMD CES (1/6), NVDA earnings (1/8), SMH flows over T+14.
  </p>
</div>

<h2 style="margin:18px 0 10px 0;">一句話結論</h2>
<blockquote style="border-left:4px solid #16a34a; padding:10px 14px; margin:0 0 14px 0; background:#f0fdf4;">
  <p style="margin:0;"><strong>這不是新品新聞，而是推理成本曲線下移的訊號。</strong>市場重算的是：雲端是否會因效能/瓦改善而前置部署。</p>
</blockquote>

<hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin:18px 0;">

