  <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:18px; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#e5e7eb;">
    <li style="margin:6px 0;"><strong>關鍵個股分析</strong>：NVDA / AMD / AVGO 的 Setup、Catalyst、Risk、估值錨點</li>
